This [[Main/en/Advanced Settings/Economy#Enable smooth economy (more, smaller changes)|Advanced Settings]] "evens out" the fluctuations in the economy.  

== Description ==

Normally, the economy only changes in large jumps (of 50%) at irregular intervals.  When this patch is enabled, there will be smaller changes at more frequent intervals.


